text: Luverne is a city in Crenshaw County, Alabama, United States. At the 2020 census the population was 2,765. The city is the county seat of Crenshaw County. ==Media== *Radio station **WHLW 104.3 FM (Gospel) *Newspaper **Luverne Journal (weekly) ==References== Category:Cities in Alabama Category:County seats in Alabama
